    <stitle>TSI 91-17-01 - Axle Flange Gasket Replacement</stitle>
    <tsi id="tsi911701" tsitype="truck">
        <tsinumber>91-17-01</tsinumber>
        <tsidate>May, 1991</tsidate>
        <subjectfile>WHEELS</subjectfile>
        <subjectgroup>
            <subject>Axle Flange Gasket Replacement</subject>
        </subjectgroup>
        <description>
            <geninfo>
                <para>Mylar axle flange gaskets are not re-usable. Mylar is a soft material that flows when placed under
                    pressure creating a gasket that is unique to the axle/hub application where it is being used. There
                    is not enough material in the gasket to allow it to be re-used and be sure that it will not leak.
                    The following information is supplied to aid in the replacement of axle hub gaskets.
                </para>
            </geninfo>
        </description>
